      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameters used in validation simulations must be demonstrated equivalent to those in the COU simulations, including fluid properties, geometric fidelity, and boundary condition types.",
      "rationale": "Validation simulations used a blood analog fluid (glycerin-water mixture) rather than actual blood rheology used in COU simulations. Equivalency of input parameters between validation and COU contexts was not formally demonstrated. Factor flagged as epistemic gap."
